title: Xbox Series X: Is This the Logo? - Kinda Funny Games Daily 04.22.20
description:
Gary Whitta and Greg talk about an apparent Xbox Series X trademark and the possibility of an Xbox Series S. 

Time Stamps - 
 00:05:25 - Housekeeping
TOMORROW night at 7 pm PT, we’re having the social event of the season: Grimecraft’s Kinda Funny Animal Crossing Rave! That’s right, Grimecraft will be DJing set in Animal Crossing for the Kinda Funny Best Friends. You can watch live -- and catch Greg interviewing Grimey after the show -- on twitch.tv/kindafunnygames. But even better, you can come to the concert IN Animal Crossing. Keep an eye on Kinda Funny’s Twitter Thursday afternoon, and you can find out how to visit Grimecraft’s island and get the exclusive in-game t-shirt.
Thank you to our Patreon Producers: Mohammed Mohammed, Al Tribesman,Black Jack
The Roper Report   -
00:07:10 - Is this the Xbox Series X Logo? Joe Skrebbels @ IGN
00:09:45 - What are your immediate thoughts? - Best Friends Q:Eamon in DC
00:26:55 - PAX West is happening?
00:38:11 - GameStop will Reopen some Stores, Brendan Sinclair @ GIB
00:42:30 - More of Far Cry 3’s Vaas on the Way? Joe FUCKING Skrebbels @ IGN
00:50:52 - Out today
Reader mail   -
00:54:35 - Could Microsoft Flight Simulator, a game that's usually used as a technical test, be paving the way as the first inkling what mid to late generation games next generation could also be like? - The Nano Biologist
01:00:55 - Squad Up: Stevie V(Animal Crossing: New Horizons) - SW-6313-4615-8126
01:02:30 - You‘re Wrong
